  "remarks": "\nKaterina Vladimirovna TIKHONOVA is widely reported to be the daughter of the President of the Russian Federation, Vladimir Vladimirovich PUTIN, with whom she is closely associated and from whom she has obtained material benefit. PUTIN is an involved person under the \nRussia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
